<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Pages on Philip Adams</title><link>https://pbada.ms/page/</link><description>Recent content in Pages on Philip Adams</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>en_US</language><atom:link href="https://pbada.ms/page/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>About</title><link>https://pbada.ms/about/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://pbada.ms/about/</guid><description>&lt;h3 id="bio"&gt;Bio
&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;I am a software engineer at &lt;a class="link" href="https://www.waymo.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
 &gt;Waymo&lt;/a&gt;. Previously, I worked on &lt;a class="link" href="https://www.bing.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
 &gt;Bing&lt;/a&gt;. Before that, I was a Math/CS student at &lt;a class="link" href="https://www.uchicago.edu" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
 &gt;UChicago&lt;/a&gt;. I&amp;rsquo;m primarily interested in systems that help us process and understand unstructured data, in particular search and example mining.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I&amp;rsquo;m also interested in aviation, photography, functional programming, and backpacking. I may touch on some of these topics on this blog, and you can see some of my photos &lt;a class="link" href="https://pbada.ms/photos" &gt;here&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id="contact"&gt;Contact
&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;You can reach me at
&lt;code&gt;blog (at) [this domain]&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I read many people&amp;rsquo;s blogs, but am always too shy to email them with questions that I have. If you&amp;rsquo;re like me, please consider this an open invitation to reach out. I&amp;rsquo;d love to hear from you!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id="disclaimer"&gt;Disclaimer
&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;Disclaimer: The opinions on this site are solely my own and do not represent the views or opinions of any of my colleagues or my employer.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Archives</title><link>https://pbada.ms/archives/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://pbada.ms/archives/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Photos</title><link>https://pbada.ms/photos/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://pbada.ms/photos/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="St. Louis, December 2016" class="gallery-image" data-flex-basis="357px" data-flex-grow="148" height="3130" loading="lazy" sizes="(max-width: 767px) calc(100vw - 30px), (max-width: 1023px) 700px, (max-width: 1279px) 950px, 1232px" src="https://pbada.ms/photos/output_berries.jpg" srcset="https://pbada.ms/photos/output_berries_hu_d0f1c58212d6e1d5.jpg 800w, https://pbada.ms/photos/output_berries_hu_99a339304799ce05.jpg 1600w, https://pbada.ms/photos/output_berries_hu_65e531c1881fdbb9.jpg 2400w, https://pbada.ms/photos/output_berries.jpg 4660w" width="4660"&gt;
